---
title: Spiced Chicken with Coconut Rice and Baked Corn on the Cob
description: This creamy coconut rice is (in our humble opinion), pretty amazing. Teamed with some delicious shawarma spiced chicken drumsticks and roasted corn on the cob, it’s going to be a sensational (but slightly messy!) dinner … Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-chicken-with-coconut-rice-f61234c1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/spiced-chicken-with-coconut-rice-433bc53c.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 782 kcal
  fat: 36 g
  saturated fat: 15 g
  carbohydrates: 62 g
  protein: 52 g
  sodium: 2 g
cuisine: Caribbean
